    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210640/extras/4b0318899f8cf28ac0867b3d8b73d307.avif?t=1756674984\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210640/extras_big/4b0318899f8cf28ac0867b3d8b73d307.avif?t=1756674984 width=800 height=264 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210640/extras/0f3634a5327e98fb14743460cf8eef72.poster.avif?t=1756674984\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210640/extras/0f3634a5327e98fb14743460cf8eef72.webm?t=1756674984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210640/extras/0f3634a5327e98fb14743460cf8eef72.mp4?t=1756674984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这款游戏与其他FNAF类作品有何不同？</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遗物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个夜晚你都会解锁新的遗物，并从中选择一个来帮助你度过黑夜。它们能带来效果，比如重置敌人，或在死亡时复活一次。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210640/extras/49887033ad4279aa7e0f3bf37cff80f8.poster.avif?t=1756674984\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210640/extras/49887033ad4279aa7e0f3bf37cff80f8.webm?t=1756674984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210640/extras/49887033ad4279aa7e0f3bf37cff80f8.mp4?t=1756674984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有电力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中没有可以消耗的电力，但这并不会让游戏更简单，因为门系统已根据这一点进行了调整。玩家不能仅仅通过开关来操作灯光或门，而是必须亲手把门按住，这迫使你停留在原地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210640/extras/46275b7a0f88232abfe4635686c6fa9d.poster.avif?t=1756674984\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210640/extras/46275b7a0f88232abfe4635686c6fa9d.webm?t=1756674984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210640/extras/46275b7a0f88232abfe4635686c6fa9d.mp4?t=1756674984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可重玩性</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次开始夜晚时，所有敌人的攻击性都会随机增加或减少。所以你永远不知道需要特别留意谁。你必须在每个夜晚进行适应，并迅速识别真正的威胁。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210640/extras/c1b79f0499aa00297eac75d9546399b2.avif?t=1756674984\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210640/extras_big/c1b79f0499aa00297eac75d9546399b2.avif?t=1756674984 width=800 height=264 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你迫切需要钱，于是接受了城里没人愿意做的工作——守卫一座位于森林深处的古老宅邸。那里没有任何通路进出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >白天无需害怕。但到了夜晚，当星象契合时，他们便会出现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在你在世界的边缘为生存而战。使用那些看似亘古存在的魔法物品并锁上大门。每个夜晚，敌人都会越来越多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过，你也会逐渐了解他们，探寻这个地方的过去。寻找线索，活下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210640/extras/fcfc805305e7c487dfca5531eb17de98.avif?t=1756674984\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210640/extras_big/fcfc805305e7c487dfca5531eb17de98.avif?t=1756674984 width=800 height=264 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Blessed with Death》自我定位为FNAF类游戏，而不是FNAF同人游戏。本作拥有独立的故事、风格与角色，与FNAF世界毫无关联。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们只是参考了最初几部FNAF作品的玩法机制，但在此基础上进行了彻底的改造。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，本作主要面向渴望新秘密与新玩法的现有社区。</p>",
